---
export const prerender = false;
import Container from "@/components/container";
import Layout from "./layout.astro";
---

<Layout subtitle="Terms of Service">
    <section class="grid place-content-center">
        <Container className="max-w-xl p-6">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">
                Terms of Service
                <p class="text-xs font-medium">Latest update: 24.05.2025</p>
            </h1>
            <p class="mb-6">
                Welcome to openshorts ("we," "our," or "us"). By accessing or
                using our website, you agree to comply with and be bound by
                these Terms of Service ("Terms") and our Privacy Policy. Please
                read them carefully. You may not use the website if you are
                under 13 years old or prohibited from using our services under
                applicable law.
            </p>
            <ol class="list-decimal space-y-6 pl-6">
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Account and Access</p>
                    <p>
                        Access to features like uploading content, liking or
                        commenting, or using AI Search requires login via GitHub
                        OAuth. You are responsible for any activity conducted
                        under your account and for maintaining its security.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">User Submissions</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>
                            <strong>Responsibility:</strong> You are solely responsible
                            for the content you submit, including links to external
                            websites or assets. Ensure that your submissions do not
                            violate any laws or infringe upon any third-party rights.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Prohibited Content:</strong> Do not submit content
                            that is unlawful, harmful, threatening, abusive, harassing,
                            defamatory, vulgar, obscene, or otherwise objectionable.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>License:</strong> By submitting content, you
                            grant us a non-exclusive, worldwide, royalty-free license
                            to use, display, and distribute your content on our platform.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Ownership:</strong> You affirm that you have
                            the legal right to share all content you submit.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Prohibited Conduct</p>
                    <p>
                        You agree not to: spam the platform, manipulate likes or
                        comments, harass users, scrape the site, attempt to
                        reverse-engineer the system, or submit malicious links.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">AI Search</p>
                    <p>
                        The AI Search feature processes your prompts to
                        recommend relevant websites submitted by users. While we
                        aim for accuracy, we do not guarantee results. Do not
                        submit confidential or sensitive information in your AI
                        prompt.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Intellectual Property</p>
                    <p>
                        All content on our website, excluding user submissions,
                        is our property or the property of our licensors and is
                        protected by intellectual property laws. You may not
                        use, reproduce, or distribute our content without our
                        prior written permission.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Termination</p>
                    <p>
                        We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access
                        to our website at our sole discretion, without notice,
                        for conduct that we believe violates these Terms or
                        harms the community or platform.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Disclaimers</p>
                    <p>
                        Our website is provided "as is" and "as available"
                        without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee the
                        accuracy, completeness, or usefulness of any content,
                        including user submissions or AI-generated results. Your
                        use of the website is at your own risk.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Limitation of Liability</p>
                    <p>
                        To the fullest extent permitted by law, we are not
                        liable for any indirect, incidental, special,
                        consequential, or punitive damages resulting from your
                        use of or inability to use our website.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Copyright Complaints</p>
                    <p>
                        If you believe content on our site infringes your
                        copyright, please email us at floyarehooked@gmail.com
                        with details. We will act in accordance with applicable
                        copyright laws.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Changes to Terms</p>
                    <p>
                        We may modify these Terms at any time. Changes become
                        effective when posted. Continued use of the site after
                        changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised
                        Terms.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Governing Law</p>
                    <p>
                        These Terms are governed by the laws of Poland, without
                        regard to its conflict of law principles.
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="font-semibold">Contact Us</p>
                    <p>
                        If you have questions about these Terms, contact us at
                        floyarehooked@gmail.com.
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </Container>
    </section>
</Layout>
